s=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534163\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ymy1665702983157.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ymy1665702983157.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ymy1665702983157.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ymy1665702983157\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      View Mode Character Mnemonics\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">These mnemonics define the characters used in View mode (for example, on the paint canvas or in a field). There are no defaults for the View mode characters. If the mnemonics are not defined, the appropriate characters from Font 7 are used.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__section_jlx_3qp_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d882333e51\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Mnemonics for View Mode Characters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">Mnemonic </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Explanation </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">view_bot</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Entity bottom line. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">view_cr</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Carriage return character. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">view_fF</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Form feed character. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">view_frame</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Frame character. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">view_ht</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Horizontal tab character. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">view_mid</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Entity middle line. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">view_top</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Entity top line. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">view_vert</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ymy1665702983157__table_d5630e1_d5631e1_d5632e1__entry__2\">Entity left or right vertical line. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__section_zxx_brp_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d882333e198\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__p_d64244e1_d64245e1_d64246e1\">These characters are usually available in a device\n        character set. If they are defined as part of a particular character set, Uniface will send\n        the control codes to shift into this character set (if it is not already in this set),\n        before displaying or printing the character.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__p_d64247e1_d64248e1_d64249e1\">For example, these mnemonics are defined as part of\n        character set 2 for a VT display. The definition for this set in the VT translation table is\n        shown below:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__pre_zff_3rp_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">BEGIN_SET 2 special GRAPHIC set\n^esc(0 select special graphic set selection\n...\nb view_ht map HT (horizontal tab)\nc view_ff map FF (formfeed)\nd view_cr map CR (carret)\no view_top map view entity top line\no view_mid map view entity mid line\ns view_bot map view entity bottom line\n~ view_vert map view entity left/right vertical\nEND_SET\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__p_d64250e1_d64251e1_d64252e1\">To output a carriage return character (identified by the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">view_cr</code> mnemonic), Uniface first sends the codes associated with the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">select</code> mnemonic for character set 2, then the character code associated\n        with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">view_cr</code> mnemonic. Therefore, for the VT device, the following\n        codes are sent to the device:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ymy1665702983157__pre_agf_3rp_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^027(0d\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534163\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534163\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "View Mode Character Mnemonics Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 View Mode Character Mnemonics These mnemonics define the characters used in View mode (for example, on the paint canvas or in a field). There are no defaults for the View mode characters. If the mnemonics are not defined, the appropriate characters from Font 7 are used. Arguments Table 1. Mnemonics for View Mode Characters Mnemonic Explanation view_bot Entity bottom line. view_cr Carriage return character. view_fF Form feed character. view_frame Frame character. view_ht Horizontal tab character. view_mid Entity middle line. view_top Entity top line. view_vert Entity left or right vertical line. Description These characters are usually available in a device character set. If they are defined as part of a particular character set, Uniface will send the control codes to shift into this character set (if it is not already in this set), before displaying or printing the character. For example, these mnemonics are defined as part of character set 2 for a VT display. The definition for this set in the VT translation table is shown below: BEGIN_SET 2 special GRAPHIC set ^esc(0 select special graphic set selection ... b view_ht map HT (horizontal tab) c view_ff map FF (formfeed) d view_cr map CR (carret) o view_top map view entity top line o view_mid map view entity mid line s view_bot map view entity bottom line ~ view_vert map view entity left/right vertical END_SET Copy To output a carriage return character (identified by the view_cr mnemonic), Uniface first sends the codes associated with the select mnemonic for character set 2, then the character code associated with the view_cr mnemonic. Therefore, for the VT device, the following codes are sent to the device: ^027(0d Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}